column5: Hi all, Finally got out in my own boat on Wednesday on my home lake. Despite unseasonal high water temps fish were pretty much where they usually are this time of year.https://youtu.be/326mqEjiaeE
Great video as always. Is the water always that dirty ?
Yup, it's all the clay, makes for really fun musky fishing, you don't see it till it's on!
Enjoyed the video, I sure would enjoy spending my summers in NWO!
